{"title":"历史的回应","authors":["吴恭让"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":9,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的回应"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴恭让"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚浪涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似无羁的烈马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏破平静。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤坝在颤抖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空前险情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上堤去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"险情就是命令。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱田垄嘉禾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更爱人民的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的心灵辉光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁出壮烈的风景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公仆，群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军，士兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天，夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电闪，雷鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢将滔滔长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当做驯马的缰绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然是狂暴的烈马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要驯在我们手中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万人的心音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答着庄严的提问；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——大地在呼应！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——历史在回应！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"答案："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么叫公仆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么叫英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是人生的价值，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是新的长城！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}